column1: The Carolina Classic Powerlifting Championship Results

Results for the Carolina Classic Held 4/10/10 Ashville, NC.  We want to Mark Ferris and Robbie Robinson for putting on a great meet, Job well done. Also want to thank all the loaders/spotters and Judges for all the help and hard work, couldn't do it without you guys, that's for sure. Matt Christie came and head Judged with Robbie and Mark on the sides. A huge thanks goes to Joey Smith for filling in for me on the mic every chance he got. Joey done a great job announcing and keeping everyone jacked up. Glad all you lifters could come out and make this a great meet and hope to see everyone at the Nationals.  Jesse Rodgers
